      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey can u explain bernoulli's principle to me? specifically how the shape of an airfoil actually creates lift. thanks",
      "source": "evaluator",
      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "hey can u explain bernoulli's principle to me? specifically how the shape of an airfoil actually creates lift. thanks",
